
* ===================================

* 題解
  * 蟬語 是 謝宇恆 設計的程序語言
    它的名字 來源與曹植的 蟬賦
      實淡泊而寡欲兮 獨咍樂而長吟
      聲噭噭而彌厲兮 似貞士之介心
  * 蟬語 以 小蟬語 爲基礎 而寫成

* 瞭解更多
  * 你可以在這裏找到更多的文檔
    http://the-little-language-designer.github.io/cicada/intro/contents.html

* 最新版本
  * 這個程序的源代碼可以在這裏下載
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada
  * archlinux 用戶可以直接安裝這裏的軟件包
    https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/cicada-git/
    或者可以直接使用如下命令 (如果你也安裝了 yaourt 的話)
      yaourt -S cicada-git

* 貢獻
  * IRC 頻道
    irc.freenode.net 服務器上的 #cicada-language
  * 郵件列表
    https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/cicada-language
  * 看版
    http://www.reddit.com/r/CicadaLanguage/
  * 維基
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/wiki
    或者
    http://www.reddit.com/r/CicadaLanguage/wiki/index

* ===================================

* to explain the title
  * cicada-language is a programming language designed by XIE Yuheng
  * the name cicada-language comes from
    the cicada rhapsody of
    the ancient Chinese prince CAO Zhi
  * cicada-language is based on cicada-nymph

* to learn more
  * you can find documentations here
    http://the-little-language-designer.github.io/cicada/intro/contents.html

* to get the newest version of the program
  * the source code of this program can be downloaded from
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada
  * archlinux user can just install the following package
    https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/cicada-git/
    or by the following command (if you have yaourt installed)
      yaourt -S cicada-git

* to contribute
  * IRC channel
    #cicada-language on irc.freenode.net
  * mailing list
    https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/cicada-language
  * reddit
    http://www.reddit.com/r/CicadaLanguage/
  * wiki
    https://github.com/the-little-language-designer/cicada/wiki
    or
    http://www.reddit.com/r/CicadaLanguage/wiki/index

